text: Gourriel is the surname of the following people *Lourdes Gourriel (born 1957), Cuban baseball player *Lourdes Gourriel Jr. or Lourdes Gurriel Jr.(born 1993), Cuban baseball player, son of Lourdes Gourriel *Yuli Gourriel or Yuli Gurriel (born 1984), Cuban baseball player, son of Lourdes Gourriel
title: Gourriel
